  "body": "### Description\r\nAs an operator, I don't want a common task like mining interruption to be logged like an error.\r\n\r\n### Acceptance Criteria\r\nMining being interrupted when a block arrives should only be visible at debug logging level.\r\n\r\n### Steps to Reproduce (Bug)\r\n1. Set up 2 besu miners.\r\n2. When one receives the new block while it is still mining, observe the ERROR message and stack trace in the logs.\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior:** [What you expect to happen]\r\nNotification of interruption should only display when DEBUG is enabled.\r\n\r\n**Actual behavior:** [What actually happens]\r\n```\r\n2022-03-23 17:22:30.511+00:00 | pool-7-thread-217 | ERROR | BlockMiner | Block mining threw an unhandled exception.\r\njava.lang.IllegalStateException: Attempt to create block was interrupted\r\n        at org.hyperledger.besu.ethereum.blockcreation.AbstractBlockCreator.createBlock(AbstractBlockCreator.java:212)\r\n        at org.hyperledger.besu.ethereum.blockcreation.AbstractBlockCreator.createBlock(AbstractBlockCreator.java:143)\r\n        at org.hyperledger.besu.ethereum.blockcreation.AbstractBlockCreator.createBlock(AbstractBlockCreator.java:129)\r\n        at org.hyperledger.besu.ethereum.blockcreation.BlockMiner.mineBlock(BlockMiner.java:136)\r\n        at org.hyperledger.besu.ethereum.blockcreation.BlockMiner.run(BlockMiner.java:83)\r\n        at java.base/java.util.concurrent.ThreadPoolExecutor.runWorker(ThreadPoolExecutor.java:1128)\r\n        at java.base/java.util.concurrent.ThreadPoolExecutor$Worker.run(ThreadPoolExecutor.java:628)\r\n        at java.base/java.lang.Thread.run(Thread.java:829)\r\nCaused by: java.util.concurrent.CancellationException\r\n        at java.base/java.util.concurrent.CompletableFuture.cancel(CompletableFuture.java:2396)\r\n        at org.hyperledger.besu.ethereum.mainnet.PoWSolver$PoWSolverJob.cancel(PoWSolver.java:65)\r\n        at java.base/java.util.Optional.ifPresent(Optional.java:183)\r\n        at org.hyperledger.besu.ethereum.mainnet.PoWSolver.cancel(PoWSolver.java:149)\r\n        at org.hyperledger.besu.ethereum.blockcreation.PoWBlockCreator.cancel(PoWBlockCreator.java:113)\r\n        at org.hyperledger.besu.ethereum.blockcreation.BlockMiner.cancel(BlockMiner.java:166)\r\n        at org.hyperledger.besu.ethereum.blockcreation.PoWMiningCoordinator.haltMiner(PoWMiningCoordinator.java:137)\r\n        at org.hyperledger.besu.ethereum.blockcreation.PoWMiningCoordinator.haltMiner(PoWMiningCoordinator.java:38)\r\n        at org.hyperledger.besu.ethereum.blockcreation.AbstractMiningCoordinator.lambda$haltCurrentMiningOperation$0(AbstractMiningCoordinator.java:164)\r\n        at java.base/java.util.Optional.ifPresent(Optional.java:183)\r\n        at org.hyperledger.besu.ethereum.blockcreation.AbstractMiningCoordinator.haltCurrentMiningOperation(AbstractMiningCoordinator.java:162)\r\n        at org.hyperledger.besu.ethereum.blockcreation.AbstractMiningCoordinator.onBlockAdded(AbstractMiningCoordinator.java:180)\r\n        at org.hyperledger.besu.ethereum.chain.DefaultBlockchain.lambda$appendBlock$9(DefaultBlockchain.java:290)\r\n        at org.hyperledger.besu.util.Subscribers.lambda$forEach$0(Subscribers.java:112)\r\n```\r\n\r\n**Frequency:** [What percentage of the time does it occur?]\r\nEvery block.\r\n\r\n",
